snippet: World number one Serena Williams wasted little time in swatting aside Russia's Margarita Gasparyan 6-2 6-1 on Sunday, setting up an Australian Open quarter-final showdown with Maria Sharapova....
lead_paragraph: World number one Serena Williams wasted little time in swatting aside Russia's Margarita Gasparyan 6-2 6-1 on Sunday, setting up an Australian Open quarter-final showdown with Maria Sharapova.

headline.print_headline: Serena Waltzes Into Australian Open Quarter-Finals
headline.main: Serena Waltzes Into Australian Open Quarter-Finals
